[ Directory publishing | Contact ]

Submit your hidden service URLs to wowanamevolatile.ch (PGP key) and I will take care of publishing them to various link directories and wikis. Price is debatable; I request at least $10 in BTC per listing (different from the previous $5 per link).

After submitting your link to directories listed below, you may wish to take the opportunity to have your link on new directories not listed yet. If you would like, I will contact you when there is a new directory available to have your link. Your links will periodically be checked for uptime; if some of them are down for a while, I may remove them from some directories depending on uptime policy.

Terms

  • While Tor hidden services (onions) are the easiest to publish, I also accept .b32.i2p addresses (eepsites or server tunnels) and Freenet keys (freesites). I'm not as comfortable with the latter two as far as where and how to list them, but bear with me and I'll figure it out. I can additionally create and attempt to submit a short url.i2p version of your .b32.i2p if you do not already have one.
  • All protocols are accepted; however HTTP, IRC, XMPP, and a few others with their own sections on hidden wikis are easier to publish.
  • Among other things, I will not accept sites with false descriptions, "bait-and-switch" sites, or man-in-the-middle "onion cloners".
  • For style and duplicity reasons, I will usually only take root site indexes (http://lb5vnwyafrlxgmlt.onion/ and not http://lb5vnwyafrlxgmlt.onion/path/to/other/service.htm). Exceptions are if the index is a hard redirect (http://zqktlwi4fecvo6ri.onion/ has a link to http://zqktlwi4fecvo6ri.onion/wiki/Main_Page) or if the services offered within one website are completely different (http://allyour4nert7pkh.onion/wiki/ and http://allyour4nert7pkh.onion/ib/).
  • Furthermore, anything I would not publish on clearnet under my nickname, I will not help you publish. I chose to use my clearnet identity for this service, and I do not wish to jeopardise myself editing wikis under this identity to add an advertisement for child rape. All entries are welcome, but I will deny them (no charge) if I do not feel safe publishing it. Again, do not falsify your site description if you feel I will not accept it. Be honest and I will consider your request like every other. Thanks for understanding.
  • I am not reliable for the content of any service I publish onto directories and wikis. I only publish links and descriptions as-is. The only thing I check a hidden service for is connectivity.
  • There will be no refunds in cases where your site was removed due to conflict with either my terms or a directory's.
